author: roosterred
title: Thrilling!
review:
Hi! I got this for my birthday and I'll tell you all about it!

First off, This set includes 4 extra darts in case they "Get lost on Mars". The darts include foam and rubber materials for safe play. Second, the distance of the darts shooting is incredible, shooting up to 20 feet. requires a bit of force to rotate the cannon, but none stressful. Last off, this blaster includes bright, vivid colors and unique design.

Concusion: could be 5$ cheaper, perfect size, a great gift that will keep you entertained for a long time!
